{"id":"4275535973","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/4275535973","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvNDI3NTUzNTk3Mw==","status":"current","title":"Configuración de servicio en Proxy de Servicios","version":{"by":{"type":"known","accountId":"712020:ef9f10ea-d622-4072-8c75-6176eaefcb76","accountType":"atlassian","email":"","publicName":"Juan Papazian","profilePicture":{"path":"/wiki/aa-avatar/712020:ef9f10ea-d622-4072-8c75-6176eaefcb76","width":48,"height":48,"isDefault":false},"displayName":"Juan Papazian","isExternalCollaborator":false,"isGuest":false,"locale":"en_US","accountStatus":"active","_expandable":{"operations":"","personalSpace":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/user?accountId=712020:ef9f10ea-d622-4072-8c75-6176eaefcb76"}},"when":"2025-10-17T19:05:34.865Z","friendlyWhen":"Oct 17, 2025","message":"","number":1,"minorEdit":false,"ncsStepVersion":"63","ncsStepVersionSource":"ncs-ack","confRev":"confluence$content$4275535973.15","contentTypeModified":false,"_expandable":{"collaborators":"","content":"/rest/api/content/4275535973"},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4275535973/version/1"}},"ancestors":[{"id":"2178416778","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2178416778","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjE3ODQxNjc3OA==","status":"current","title":"Bancard","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":878},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2178416778/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2178416778","tinyui":"/x/igDYgQ","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2178416778","webui":"/spaces/BAN/overview","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2178416778"}},{"id":"2261450763","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/2261450763","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMjI2MTQ1MDc2Mw==","status":"current","title":"Infrastructure","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":274390946},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2261450763/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2261450763","tinyui":"/x/CwDLhg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2261450763","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2261450763/Infrastructure","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2261450763"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<p>Para configurar un servicio en el proxy de servicios (10.100.14.73), es necesario configurar 2 cosas:</p><ul><li><p>nginx</p></li><li><p>iptables</p></li></ul><h1>Configuraci&oacute;n de NGINX</h1><p>Para la configuraci&oacute;n de nginx, se debe crear y/o modificar los siguientes archivos dentro de <strong>/etc/nginx/</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>sites-available/*.conf</p></li><li><p>sites-enable/*.conf (<em>links simb&oacute;licos a sites-available de los que se quiera habilitar</em>)</p></li><li><p>conf.d/*.conf&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>sudo nginx -t // verificar que la configuraci&oacute;n sea correcta</p></li><li><p>sudo -s reload </p></li></ul><p>Para dicha configuraci&oacute;n, lo ideal es basarse en otro servicio que ya tenga configurado nginx, como jPOS o Fingerprint. </p><h2><strong>Puertos - Configuraci&oacute;n&nbsp;</strong></h2><p>Se pueden ver las reglas de iptables con el siguiente comando:&nbsp;</p><ul><li><p>&nbsp;sudo iptables -L -n // por defecto muestra la tabla <em>filter</em></p></li></ul><p>En este paso, se deben agregar nuevas reglas para los nuevos puertos que abrimos al configurar nginx y que queramos habilitar. Por ejemplo se debe permitir el acceso al puerto 4499, el cual se corresponde con el puerto de la API de Docker configurado en el paso anterior. Para eso se debe agregar la siguiente regla a trav&eacute;s del comando <strong>sudo vim /etc/sysconfig/iptables</strong>:</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><code># Rule for docker 4499 - Docker API</code></p><p><code>-A INPUT -m state --state NEW -m tcp -p tcp --dport 4499 -j ACCEPT</code></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Luego de modificar el archivo de configuraci&oacute;n de iptables se debe ejecutar el comando <strong>sudo systemctl reload iptables</strong> para que tome la configuraci&oacute;n nueva.</p>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4275535973"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":2166},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/4275535973/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/4275535973/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/4275535973/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/4275535973/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=4275535973","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/4275535973/Configuraci+n+de+servicio+en+Proxy+de+Servicios","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/4275535973","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/4275535973","tinyui":"/x/ZYDX-g","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}